Description.SourceString: He steps onto the stage and the music stops. Adorning his elaborate costume, he takes a moment to address the crowd and devotes the song to his previous band members. The grieving crowd cheers and the music starts.
It was his last weekend in New York City before returning home and he was determined to make it memorable.
